## ğŸ§  About the Project

**LEAF (Learning Emotions via Adaptive Feedback)** is an open-source framework that integrates **emotional modeling** into reinforcement learning agents.  
It aims to explore how emotions such as curiosity, frustration, and confidence can shape adaptive behaviors and decision-making in AI.

